			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-16 08:34:24 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/14963/medium/14963.jpg?1442328486" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="14963" data-title="《在这个“贝壳”里演奏吧，坐在海边的人都能听见你的音乐》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/14963/medium/14963.jpg?1442328486" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/14963.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
